# Terraform: state holds generated secret material — NEVER commit it.
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/tfplan*
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Real var/secret files — keep only the *.example.
**/*.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example
**/secrets.env
!**/secrets.env.example

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
